{"_type": "event", "_id": "ocd-event/16d74a3c-6e40-f26d-534a-11e5161b7b36", "updated_at": "2025-10-31T04:00:06.484327-04:00", "name": "Board of Police Commissioners Meeting - January 11, 2024", "description": "The Detroit Board of Police Commissioners has scheduled a meeting for Thursday, January 11, 2024 at 6:30 p.m., at Northwest Activities Center, 18100 Meyers Road, in the 12th Precinct area.\n\n \n\nPresenter/Topic:\n\nNeighborhood & Community Updates and Recognitions\n2023 & 2024 Crime Statistics\nPublic Hearing on DPD Policy \nEyewitness Identification and Lineups - Manual Directive 203.11\n\n \n\nWith advance notice of seven calendar days, the City of Detroit will provide interpreter services at public meetings, including language translation and reasonable ADA accommodations. Please contact the Civil Rights, Inclusion, and Opportunity Department at (313) 224-4950,  TTY number 711, or crio@detroitmi.gov to schedule these services.\n\n \n\nThe public may attend in person or on Zoom Meeting ID 81981390642 \n\nZoom Link\n\n \n\nBy telephone, call one of these numbers:\n1 (267) 831-0333        1 (346) 248-7799\n1 (301) 715-8592        1 (253) 215-8782       \n\nEnter the BOPC Meeting ID 81981390642 and press ##\n\nTo sign up online to speak for two minutes during Oral Communications, go to\nhttps://app.smartsheet.com/b/form/d26fa38cc5e94a018836d065000714ce", "classification": "Board", "status": "passed", "all_day": false, "start_time": "2024-01-11T13:30:00-05:00", "end_time": null, "timezone": "America/Detroit", "location": {"url": "", "name": "Detroit Public Safety Headquarters", "coordinates": null}, "documents": [], "links": [{"url": "https://detroitmi.gov/sites/detroitmi.localhost/files/events/2024-01/Agenda%20January%2011%2C%202024_0.pdf", "title": "Agenda"}, {"url": "https://detroitmi.gov/sites/detroitmi.localhost/files/events/2024-01/Approved%20Minutes%20December%2021%2C%202023.pdf", "title": "Minutes"}, {"url": "https://detroitmi.gov/sites/detroitmi.local